{"tid":1742684,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"呢幾日既重點係區選，其他事唔做幾日不影響大局","createTime":"2019-11-21T01:35:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T09:22:32.000Z","uid":76310,"like":25,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"27b32c0c92332542459edd87c379a6e502b93375","tid":1742684,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:35:37.000Z","msg":"呢呢幾日既重點係區選，其他事唔做幾日不影響大局<br />\n<br />\n區選是重要的，至少係民意係間接或直接表現，如果比奶共派贏左，比奶共派話民意係佢地果邊<br />\n支持正苦既人係大多數<br />\n到時正苦不斷話佢地先係民意 外國有什麼干預 制裁或幫助 正苦用呢個做盾牌擋晒會好大獲<br />\n<br />\n我已經唔講控制地區資源<br />\n控制特首既票呢d<br />\n<br />\n所以做休息撚全力做區選根本問題不大<br />\n遲幾日會死？ <br />\n唔好意氣用事，起碼贏左區選先，以後話民意在我方，做所有野合情合理好多<br />\n<br />\n請用你的方法做好區選<br />\n唔好攪其他野住 只做區選 星期四五六日 只係4日時間 贏選票贏席位 以後做什麼都出師有功<br />\n希望大家明我講什麼 這四天只做區選相關既野 其他唔好做"},{"pid":"c52a47698709acf6ee48bc864a661fc2e5219968","tid":1742684,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:37:17.000Z","msg":"咁理大啲手足點呀？都要救呀！"},{"pid":"668c05bfe60b1b705d2d886b01090513ad6fa0cf","tid":1742684,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:37:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4477fd8ee4de5d4aaa6b63849b218d96f55cac76","tid":1742684,"uid":28432,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:37:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6631a1a5e77c3caeccadf7a92011da3e1a51d435","tid":1742684,"uid":78184,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:55:26.000Z","msg":"重點區選，搶奪保皇政治資源"},{"pid":"2fc7943412623c1d89d1d920b3a202e211c065dd","tid":1742684,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:55:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5782b8d99ffb80fd370b72967a2fa6625b316933","tid":1742684,"uid":151924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:56:47.000Z","msg":"好文幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n努力做返好文宣先"},{"pid":"8d46065a475933738a3af16dff6bc185bf903a01","tid":1742684,"uid":151924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:57:55.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e46dd9e9e885887e795cd23c5f894cb5d38950a","tid":1742684,"uid":306826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:59:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">星期日記住投票</span></span><br />\n阻你地少少時間 有關選舉問題可以睇以下post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n0成本截斷建制藍絲收入 (下)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742026</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"30ed4a94a097d893b60c4e38a5441ef5bbc776e4","tid":1742684,"uid":65738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:02:07.000Z","msg":"不要說<span style=\"color: red;\">大局</span>, 請戒掉蝗語壞習慣，要說<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">局勢/ 形勢</span></span>"},{"pid":"22b53002548305643fd165f557f42e1f1c68271f","tid":1742684,"uid":76310,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:08:35.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n用自己方法攪好區選"},{"pid":"d8a1d08aee3c7b7e5e0cba2a9dcda5d6b6c3e98a","tid":1742684,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:44:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7c50dfc4481bfce373e740da580d0127097ee83","tid":1742684,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:32:49.000Z","msg":"民意係一張好重要既牌"},{"pid":"5fc7eaf6c1afd7d24ed2ddb59c57a45877413209","tid":1742684,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:53:39.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n4日影響到大局咩<br />\n區選都係抗爭方法之一"},{"pid":"694c9b6b29ba2860b79cf9696611d44ed231babf","tid":1742684,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:54:08.000Z","msg":"香港金融業職工總會（香港金總）將於星期六舉行特別會員大會，以商討政治工業行動事宜。本會已根據香港金總會章，於2019年11月18日以電郵通知本會會員召開特別會員大會事宜。詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n特別會員大會<br />\n日期：2019年11月23日<br />\n時間：下午5時至8時<br />\n地點：尖沙咀金巴利道25號長利商業大廈12樓1202室<br />\n備註：<br />\n -  請出席之會員提早15分鐘前來登記，以便準時開始。<br />\n -  會場內，除大會攝影師外，不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzqZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=594e5426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzqZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=21477f51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzqZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=3e89dbbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzqZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=3d4cfeb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會"},{"pid":"cbc817c21275af5d8b435ffee13fd7207a9ad1d7","tid":1742684,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:25:04.000Z","msg":"區選呀"},{"pid":"99a923dd3dd7f7103154be7c6ca08da7d206da0c","tid":1742684,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbc817c21275af5d8b435ffee13fd7207a9ad1d7","tid":1742684,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:25:04.000Z","msg":"區選呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:26:36.000Z","msg":"同五大訴求有咩關係<br />\n冇區選對運動有咩影響"},{"pid":"1a1f06b813f3c6fb77330a600fefca44